OFF THE CHARTS.

29:12.881 --> 29:14.491
I'’M TALKING
PENELOPE GARCIA LEVEL.

29:14.535 --> 29:16.145
CHANNING:
WELL, THAT NARROWS
THE SUSPECT POOL.

29:16.189 --> 29:17.407
