31:46.992 --> 31:49.646
ASMR, SUSCEPTIBILITY
TO TACTILE STIMULATION,

31:49.690 --> 31:50.952
SUBLIMINAL MESSAGING,

31:50.996 --> 31:52.693
PLUS, THEY'’RE AT
THE MOST VULNERABLE AGE

31:52.736 --> 31:54.303
