MOLESTING THEM.

32:29.338 --> 32:31.166
SO ONCE THE GOSSIP
MACHINE REVVED UP,

32:31.210 --> 32:32.689
IT DIDN'’T SLOW DOWN.

32:32.733 --> 32:33.995
