33:32.097 --> 33:35.404
HOW OLD IS HE?
OR IS IT A SHE?

33:35.448 --> 33:38.103
HE'’S A LITTLE BOY,
AND HE'’S ALMOST 8 MONTHS OLD.

33:38.146 --> 33:42.716
