33:52.030 --> 33:53.509
WHY HURT YOUR BOY?

33:53.553 --> 33:55.250
WHY DO SUCH TERRIBLE,

33:55.294 --> 33:59.124
UNTHINKABLE
THINGS TO HIM?

33:59.167 --> 34:01.430
BECAUSE THAT'’S
WHAT I HEARD

34:01.474 --> 34:05.695
FROM YOUR NEIGHBORS,
YOUR FRIENDS,

34:05.739 --> 34:08.176
