YOU COULD TRUST,

34:08.220 --> 34:12.180
THE SAME WAY ALL OF YOU
TALKED ABOUT ME.

34:12.224 --> 34:13.616
LEAVE ME ALONE.

34:14.965 --> 34:16.097
