A ROOF BEAM.

34:36.117 --> 34:38.467
MATT SAID THAT HOLLIS'’
SON GARRETT HAD BEEN TEASED

34:38.511 --> 34:41.731
AND TORMENTED
IN SCHOOL OVER RUMORS
SURROUNDING HIS FATHER.

34:41.775 --> 34:43.081
