35:00.533 --> 35:02.970
HOLLIS: I'’M SERIOUS.
DON'’T MOVE, PEOPLE!

35:03.013 --> 35:06.234
DO NOT MOVE!
RUN AWAY, I KILL HER.

35:06.278 --> 35:08.671
WAYNE HOLLIS, FBI.

35:08.715 --> 35:10.760
LET HER GO.
DROP THE WEAPON.

35:10.804 --> 35:11.935
HOLLIS: NO, NO, NO, NO.

35:11.979 --> 35:14.503
EVERYBODY IN THIS TOWN
TALKS EXCEPT ME.

35:14.547 --> 35:18.028
GOSSIP, RUMOR,
INNUENDO.

35:18.072 --> 35:20.770
YOU THINK I HURT
YOUR CHILDREN,

35:20.814 --> 35:23.164
