WANT YOU TO REACT.

35:31.520 --> 35:33.348
IT DOESN'’T MATTER
WHAT GARRETT WANTS
OR DOESN'’T WANT.

35:33.392 --> 35:34.697
HE'’S DEAD,

35:34.741 --> 35:36.917
BECAUSE OF YOU,

35:36.960 --> 35:38.571
ALL OF YOU.

35:38.614 --> 35:41.356
HE HAD HOPES
AND DREAMS,

35:41.400 --> 35:44.620
AND YOU TOOK IT ALL
AWAY WITH YOUR LIES.

35:44.664 --> 35:46.361
LIES!

35:46.405 --> 35:51.018
WELL, NOW I'’M
TAKING SOMETHING
AWAY FROM YOU.

35:51.061 --> 35:53.934
