AMINO ACIDS FOUND
IN COMPLEX PROTEINS.

36:46.204 --> 36:47.901
IT'’S COMMONLY FOUND
IN MEAT TENDERIZERS.

36:47.944 --> 36:49.468
GARCIA.

36:49.511 --> 36:50.860
UH...

36:50.904 --> 36:52.732
