THE COUNTRY,

38:54.767 --> 38:57.770
GRANDKIDS RUNNING
ALL AROUND,

38:57.813 --> 39:00.338
FOOD COOKING
IN THE KITCHEN.

39:01.774 --> 39:03.602
THAT SOUNDS NICE.

39:03.645 --> 39:08.868
YEAH. EXCEPT IT WAS
ALL MAKE-BELIEVE.

39:08.911 --> 39:11.610
