STUPID MOVIE

39:11.653 --> 39:14.656
IN THE TRASH FOR GOOD.

39:14.700 --> 39:17.137
I BLAMED YOUR FATHER.

39:17.180 --> 39:19.139
I BLAMED MYSELF.

39:19.182 --> 39:23.448
I BLAMED THE WHOLE
DAMN WORLD.

39:23.491 --> 39:26.320
I GOT SO CAUGHT UP
