41:21.653 --> 41:23.872
YEAH, I WILL.

41:23.916 --> 41:27.136
UH, SPENCE, HAVE YOU...

41:27.180 --> 41:29.791
HAVE YOU EVER PROJECTED
YOURSELF

41:29.835 --> 41:32.315
INTO AN IMAGINED FUTURE?

41:32.359 --> 41:34.317
YOU KNOW, GIVEN THAT
PARTICLES CAN TRAVEL

41:34.361 --> 41:35.884
